He said, no, it's $750.

14:25.293 --> 14:27.037
He said, no, it's $750.

14:27.297 --> 14:29.401
He says, well, how about $550?

14:29.421 --> 14:31.645
And I said, go buy it someplace else.

14:31.996 --> 14:33.719
And just out of principle, I would never do that.

14:34.000 --> 14:37.507
And then the guy finally confessed to me, said, listen, I'm fairly new here.

14:37.527 --> 14:41.855
I'm only 22 years old, and I thought it would be good if I could buy it and it would look good on my record.

14:41.915 --> 14:43.198
We don't do that as a rule.

14:43.499 --> 14:48.829
I have clients that make enormous purchases who are very consistent that I would spend a 10% discount to.

14:48.909 --> 14:52.236
Which is kind of standard.

14:52.376 --> 14:52.917
Yeah, right.

14:52.937 --> 14:54.460
But that's it.

14:54.608 --> 14:59.473
