15:09.122 --> 15:11.845
Oh, yeah, and if I say, gee, did you know that this is missing a leaf?

15:12.225 --> 15:15.068
Well, then I was definitely making a justification.

15:15.148 --> 15:17.671
Yeah, the spine is cracked like daddy goes off.

15:17.691 --> 15:19.593
That doesn't happen.

15:19.693 --> 15:22.756
No, but I think everybody is flexible.

15:22.776 --> 15:24.177
I think it's important to be flexible.

15:24.595 --> 15:28.480
Some people are fairly stubborn about it, and I think it's silly.

15:28.540 --> 15:31.585
Is the L.A.

15:31.605 --> 15:40.357
collective a distinctive, I was going to say, unique creature?

15:40.437 --> 15:43.601
Well, a lot of income.

15:43.661 --> 15:47.306
In many cases made quickly over the last couple of years.

15:49.329 --> 15:51.131
I have 7,000 people on my mailing list.

15:51.212 --> 15:52.273
I'll bet you at least

