16:10.712 --> 16:14.316
I know at least 10 customers that are worth a half a billion dollars that are on my mailing list.

16:14.416 --> 16:18.480
Half a billion would be 500 million dollars.

16:18.781 --> 16:20.804
Yeah, it doesn't matter.

16:20.864 --> 16:24.831
You know, it doesn't matter because, no, they're not people coming every week and visit me.

16:24.851 --> 16:29.018
I mean, people, most, the richer they are, the less often I see them.

16:29.038 --> 16:31.382
That doesn't, and more often I don't work directly with them.

16:31.722 --> 16:34.547
The biggest customers I have, I don't even work with them, to tell you the truth.

16:34.567 --> 16:39.255
I meet them once, I meet their librarian, their assistant, their assistants are their assistants.

16:39.275 --> 16:39.375
Yeah.

16:40.857 --> 16:42.460
But I don't mind them.

16:44.093 --> 16:45.395
One or two other questions.

16:45.415 --> 16:46.637
Tell me about the Gutenberg.

16:47.098 --> 16:52.065
There's a stained-glass window where you and your brother are represented in it.

16:52.105 --> 16:53.648
Tell me a little bit about that.

16:53.668 --> 17:02.401
Well, actually, that's described in the brochure, but basically it's... But the brochure doesn't say that you and Ben are pictured there.

17:02.422 --> 17:03.764
I think it does.

17:03.924 --> 17:06.608
