17:17.977 --> 17:18.658
But that was just it.

17:18.919 --> 17:25.871
When we put this place together, we were trying to do something a little different, because there's so little creativity in our business, that's all.

17:26.452 --> 17:30.098
And I think we've accomplished that, because it is a different feeling.

17:30.601 --> 17:38.771
And you'll come in here on the Saturdays and we have a lot of our regulars in here who come in every Saturday and they'll spend $500 to $5,000 and they're professional people.

17:39.472 --> 17:49.524
