22:38.726 --> 22:39.828
Of course, it is valuable.

22:40.469 --> 22:41.069
Well, it's great.

22:41.370 --> 22:42.532
It's the future.

22:42.552 --> 22:46.817
It's great because it would be dramatically different and exciting.

22:46.838 --> 22:49.882
We would then have virtually unlimited funds to buy at auction.

22:49.902 --> 22:50.563
We wouldn't have to work.

22:50.783 --> 22:55.149
It was well restricted by availability of cash flow, you know, and things like that.

